176 A.3d 210 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. PIERRE A. DENEUS, A/K/A HARRY JEAN-PIERRE, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-377 September Term 2017

079676 November 30, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003133-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
